<h3>Submission Guidelines</h3>
<hr/>
<p>
Create a new Submission and set a maximun of 3 other co Authors, each co Author to be considered need a different email in the form.
After submission you will receive an email with the log in credentials
After filling up the form then you have to proceed to upload the file in PDF format, this can be done by selecting the Upload File option that appers inmediatly after submitting the article or
log in to the system and go to the "Submited By Author" tab.
You can see in what status your submission is in the "Submited By Author" tab, you will receive the reviews by email, you can then log back and address any criticism and re-submit your file, you can only re submit twice, so its better to wait until you receive the 3 emails that contain the reviews.
After this proccess is done the editor will receive the 3 reviews and examine the results, if he decides to publish your submission you will receive an email.
Now that your submission is published you have to log back and select 3 papers to review. After finishing your 3 reviews you just have to wait for the editor decidion on this papers, when he decides to publish or reject the papers in which you have been involved
then your article is ready to appear in the next issue.
You can only have 1 submission at a time.
</p>
